                     <interp inst="t18180909-232-person1756" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming out of my house and heard the prosecutor say there he goes with my bundle. The prisoner was running, he passed me, I followed him through a passage into a little court, where he dropped the bundle. I took him. I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard the alarm, and was taken.</p>
